snippet.title: Animal Jam! | Play for Free!
snippet.description:
Welcome to Animal Jam!
Join millions of others and become your favorite animal! Inside the beautiful 3D world of Jamaa, you can play as a wolf, bunny, cat - anything you choose! You can customize your animal from head to tail with all sorts of colors and accessories. You’ll be able to play tons of various games, decorate your own den, adopt awesome pets, explore different landscapes, create amazing works of art, and meet new friends every day. Animal Jam is a safe place and the best online community for kids.

Play Animal Jam for free here: https://www.animaljam.com/en
